Beauty Point is near the Northern Coast of Tasmania on the west of the Tamar.

This place firstly has an aquarium like room where it has tanks with specimens of many different types of seahorse, before moving onto the second room where seahorses are produced on a truly industrial scale, primarily to supply research and home aquariums.  You can see many of them in all stages of development.  Unless you are really into seahorses, you may find the final room with a touch pool, crabs, and many other sea creatures the most interesting.
